[SIZE=5][B][COLOR=#ef6c00]Commands[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]

[TABLE]
[TR]
[TH]Command[/TH]
[TH]Description[/TH]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/leaftree generate species=<id>[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Place a tree at your cursor (admin test)[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/leaftree give species=<id> [player] [amount][/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Hand out custom saplings[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/leaftree list [species=<id>][/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]List registered species or variants[/TD]
[/TR]
[TR]
[TD][ICODE]/leaftree reload[/ICODE][/TD]
[TD]Apply config changes and regenerate the datapack[/TD]
[/TR]
[/TABLE]

Requires the [ICODE]leaftreegen.admin[/ICODE] permission node.

[HR][/HR]

[SIZE=5][B][COLOR=#6a1b9a]Configuration[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]

Species are defined as JSON files in the [ICODE]species/[/ICODE] folder. Biome assignments and placement tuning (spacing, separation, salt) live in [ICODE]config.yml[/ICODE], with per-species overrides.

[CODE=yaml]
generation-mode: DATAPACK   # DATAPACK | PROCEDURAL | BOTH | NONE

placement:
  glacierpine:
    spacing: 6
    separation: 3
    biomes:
      - minecraft:snowy_taiga
      - minecraft:grove
[/CODE]

[CODE=json]
{
  "name": "glacierpine",
  "procedural": {
    "trunk-block": "minecraft:spruce_log",
    "leaf-block": "minecraft:spruce_leaves",
    "height-min": 10,
    "height-max": 18,
    "trunk-shape": "LINEAR",
    "canopy": [
      { "yOffset": 0, "radius": 4 },
      { "yOffset": 3, "radius": 3 },
      { "yOffset": 6, "radius": 2 }
    ]
  }
}
[/CODE]

[SIZE=5][B][COLOR=#00838f]Requirements[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]

[LIST]
[*]Java 25+
[*]One of:
[LIST]
[*]Paper or Folia 1.21+
